D. Acquisition Strategy
The MDA will employ a flexible and adaptive range of contracting strategies to maximize benefits, leveraging industry partnerships, competitive procurements, Broad
Agency Announcements, Small Business Innovative Research programs, Federally Funded Research and Development Centers, University Affiliated Research Centers,
and collaborations with Other Government Agencies. This approach will draw on Agency and Partner subject matter expertise to inform acquisition decisions, enabling
rapid response to changing needs, adaptation to evolving requirements, and capitalization on emerging opportunities.




