- Continue flight testing of prototype hardware and software.
- Validate exit criteria and technical performance parameters.
- Finalize plans to deliver the final design package for transition to the Program of Record.

Advanced Autonomous Air-to-Air Refueling System (A4RS)
- This FNC was completed in FY24 rather than being continued, as it was determined the capability is early to
